title: Did First COVID-19 Vaccine Recipient Suspiciously Appear in News Report Months Earlier?
subtitle: A right-wing social media activist saw evidence of conspiracy where there was none in photographs of Margaret Keenan from December 2020.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Margaret Keenan, the first recipient of the Pfizer/BioNTech COVID-19 vaccine in December 2020, was featured in a news report two months earlier, providing evidence of wrongdoing or deception.
